<div class="com-share" data-id="3105" data-title="《今日应用：Heyday 用照片写日记》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3105/medium/3105.jpg?1436636425" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3105.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
